quran[49]{c,v,t}:
  52,1,"Mede Bepͻ Tuur (a Mene Mose kasaa wͻ soͻ),"
  52,2,"Ne Nwoma a yatwerε-"
  52,3,"Wͻ nwoma a yatrε mu soͻ,"
  52,4,"Ne Efie no a ( Soro abͻfoͻ) twa ho hyia,"
  52,5,"Ne (ͻsoro) nkurusoͻ a yapagya,"
  52,6,"Ne ͻpo a nsuo ayiri ayε mma (anaasε ͻpo a egya bεtͻ mu wͻ Atemmuda) no di nse sε:"
  52,7,"“Nokorε, wo Wura Nyankopͻn asotwee no besi ampa."
  52,8,"Na enni obia obetumi asi ano kwan."
  52,9,"Ɛda a ͻsoro bεwoso nwosoeε paa no,"
  52,10,"Na mmepͻ betutu afri hͻ tutu paa no,"
  52,11,"Saa Da no due nka wͻn a wͻfaa nokorε no atorᴐsԑm no,"
  52,12,"Wͻn a wͻde ahuhudeε na εgye wͻn ani no."
  52,13,"Ɛda no a yεbepia wͻn wͻ ͻhyε so akͻ Amanehunu gya no mu no,"
  52,14,"(Yεbεka akyerε wͻn sε): “Ogya no a na moka sε εyε nkontompo no nie."
  52,15,"Woi yε nkonyaa anaa naadaasεm, anaasε monhunu?”"
  52,16,"Monhye wͻ mu; sε mosi aboterε o, sε monsi aboterε o, εyε asεm korͻ mamo. Dwuma a modiiε no ara ho akatua na yεde tua moka."
  52,17,"Nokorε sε Nyamesurofoͻ no benya Aheman ne anigyeε."
  52,18,"Wͻbεgye wͻn ani wͻ deε wͻn Wura Nyankopͻn de ama wͻn no ho; (efrisε) wͻn Wura ayi wͻn afri Amane hunu gya asotwee no mu."
  52,19,"“Monfa anigyeε nnidi na monom wͻ dwuma (pa) a modiiε no ho”."
  52,20,"Wͻbεgyegye adamu wᴐ ahennwa a yahyehyε no santen so; na yεde ‘Huur’ (ͻsoro aheman mu mmaa no a) wͻn ani mma akεse-akεse fεfεεfε bεka wͻn ho."
  52,21,"Wͻn a wagye adie na wͻn mma dii wͻn akyi wͻ gyidie mu no, Yεde wͻn mma no bεka wͻn ho; na Yεnte hwee mfri wͻn dwumadie akatua no so. Yεde onipa biara kraa asi awowa ama dwuma a nensa diiε."
  52,22,"Yεbεma nnuaba ne εnam, emu deε εyε wͻn akͻnnͻ biara abu wͻn so."
  52,23,"Nkuruwa (a nsa pa) a εmma ahuhusεm anaa εmfa bͻne mma befri woi hͻ akͻ woi hͻ."
  52,24,"Mmeranteε asomfoͻ a wͻ’yε wͻn dea, wͻ’te sε nhwene pa a yεde asie, betwa wͻn ho ahyia (asom wͻn)."
  52,25,"Wͻbεdane wͻn ho de wͻn anim ahwε wͻn ho anim abisa."
  52,26,"Wͻbεka sε: “Kane a na yεwͻ y’abusuafoͻ mu no (nyinaa) na yesuro (Nyankopͻn abufuo ne N’asotwee no)."
  52,27,"Enti Nyankopͻn adom yεn, εna Wayi yεn afri (Amanehunu gya) mframa hyehyeε no mu."
  52,28,"Nokorε sε, kanee no yesu frεε no. Nokorε sε Ͻyε Otumfoͻ a Ɔwͻ ayεmyε, Ɔne Mmͻborͻhunufoͻ Hene no."
  52,29,"Enti (Nkͻmhyεni), wodeε tu (amanfoͻ no) fo; na wo Wura Nyankopͻn adom ho nti no wonnyε pε-adeε-hununi anaa ͻbͻdamfoͻ."
  52,30,"Anaasε wͻ’ka sε (Nkͻmhyεni) yε ͻdwomtoni, enti montwεn no wͻ mmusuo berε bi mu?"
  52,31,"(Nkͻmhyεni), ka sε: “Montwεn, na menso meka mo ne wͻn a wͻretwεn no ho“."
  52,32,"Anaasε wͻn adwen na εhyε wͻn saa, anaasε wͻyε nnipa a wͻ’te atua?"
  52,33,"Anaasε wͻ’ka sε, (Nkͻmhyεni) no ara na abͻ netrim (atwerε Qur’aan no)? Daabi, gye na wͻnnye nnie."
  52,34,"Ɛneε wͻn mfa asεm bi a εte saa mmra sε wͻyε nokwafoͻ ampa a."
  52,35,"Anaasε εnyε biribi mu na yεbͻͻ wͻn fire? Anaasε wͻn ara ne Ɔbͻͻ adeε no?"
  52,36,"Anaasε wͻn na wͻ’bͻͻ soro ne asaase? Daabi, gye na wͻ’nnye nnie."
  52,37,"Anaasε wo Wura Nyankopͻn akoradeε no wͻ wͻn hͻ? Anaasε wͻn wͻ so tumi?"
  52,38,"Anaasε wͻn wͻ atwedeε (a wͻde foro kͻ soro) kotie (Soro abͻfoͻ no, ne deε εrekͻso wͻhͻ)? Ɛneε wͻn atiefoͻ no mfa wͻn nyinasoͻ pefee mmra."
  52,39,"Anaasε (Nyankopͻn) wͻ mma mmaa εna monso mowͻ mma mmarima?"
  52,40,"Anaasε (Nkͻmhyεni) wobisa wͻn akatua εna εka no mu ayε duduudu ama wͻn?"
  52,41,"Anaasε Asumade (anaasε) Ahuntasεm no wͻ wͻn hͻ na wͻ’twerε to hͻ?"
  52,42,"Anaasε wͻ’pε sε wͻbͻ pͻ (bͻne) bi (tia Nkͻmhyεni)? Ɛneε wͻn a wͻ’nnye nnie no ara na wͻbεtͻ fidie no mu."
  52,43,"Anaasε wͻn wͻ awurade foforͻ bi ka Nyankopͻn ho? Kronkron Hene ne Nyankopͻn, Ɔkorͻn kyεn deε wͻde bata Neho no."
  52,44,"Sε wͻrehunu ͻsoro no fa bi sε εrete ahweε a, anka wͻ’bεka sε: “Mununkum a ano aboa’’."
  52,45,"Enti (Nkͻmhyεni), wodeε gyae wͻn kosi sε wͻbehyia wͻn Da no a (ehu ne suro) bεma wͻn atwitwa ahwe ama adeε atͻ wͻn soͻ no."
  52,46,"Ɛda no a wͻn pͻ a wͻbͻeε no ho mma mfasoͻ biara mma wͻn, na obiara mmoa wͻn no."
  52,47,"Nokorε sε wͻn a wͻdi bͻne no san wͻ asotwee foforͻ (wͻ wiase ha); nanso nnipa pii nnim."
  52,48,"Enti (Nkͻmhyεni), wodeε si aboterε fama wo Wura Nyankopͻn atemmuo no, na nokorε sε wo wͻ Y’ani so (anaasε Yehu wo anaa Yεbͻ woho ban); na bͻ wo Wura Nyankopͻn abodin wͻ εberε a wobεsͻre (afri nna mu),"
  52,49,"Na fa anadwo no mu bi nso bͻ no abodin, na εberε a nsoromma bεkͻ akͻtͻ no nso (bͻ no abodin)."
